author: jdcasey
msg: Fixing issue with different lifecycles getting in the way of one another, as when `mvn clean install` on a maven-plugin project catches the clean:clean binding from the clean lifecycle, and knocks out the plugin:descriptor binding from the beginning of the default lifecycle.
Plugins can now be built using maven trunk once again.
